### 01 订单基础流程自测
### 目标：验证 Gateway 鉴权、订单查询、订单状态机推进。
### 前置：基础设施和后端服务已启动，Nacos 配置已导入。
### 网关地址：http://[::1]:8080

@baseUrl = http://[::1]:8080
@seedOrderNo = ORD2026051000001

### 1. 登录获取 Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=admin&password=123456

> {%
    client.test("登录成功", function () {
        client.assert(response.status === 200, "HTTP 状态应为 200");
        client.assert(response.body.code === 200, "业务 code 应为 200");
        client.assert(!!response.body.data.access_token, "应返回 data.access_token");
    });
    client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.data.access_token);
%}

### 2. 未带 Token 查询订单，预期被网关拦截
GET {{baseUrl}}/order/{{seedOrderNo}}

> {%
    client.test("未授权请求被拦截", function () {
        client.assert(response.status === 401, "未带 Token 应返回 401");
    });
%}

### 3. 带 Token 查询种子订单
GET {{baseUrl}}/order/{{seedOrderNo}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

> {%
    client.test("种子订单查询成功", function () {
        client.assert(response.status === 200, "HTTP 状态应为 200");
        client.assert(response.body.code === 200, "业务 code 应为 200");
        client.assert(response.body.data.orderNo === "ORD2026051000001", "订单号应匹配");
    });
%}

### 4. 推进种子订单状态机
### 首次从 CREATED -> PROCESSING；如果你重复运行，可能继续推进到 WAIT_EXTERNAL_SYNC / PENDING_PAYMENT / SETTLED / CLOSED。
POST {{baseUrl}}/order/advance
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

orderNo={{seedOrderNo}}

> {%
    client.test("订单状态推进成功", function () {
        client.assert(response.status === 200, "HTTP 状态应为 200");
        client.assert(response.body.code === 200, "业务 code 应为 200");
        client.assert(!!response.body.data.status, "应返回推进后的订单状态");
    });
%}

### 5. 再次查询确认状态已变化
GET {{baseUrl}}/order/{{seedOrderNo}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
